    'Authorship must reflect genuine intellectual contribution to the research. Honorary or gift authorship is prohibited. All contributors must be appropriately acknowledged.': '作者身份必须反映对研究的真实智识贡献。禁止荣誉署名或赠予署名。所有贡献者均应得到适当致谢。',
    'Conflicts of interest may be financial (e.g., funding relationships, equity stakes, consulting arrangements), personal (e.g., family or close personal relationships), or professional (e.g., competitive relationships, prior commitments).': '利益冲突可能是财务性的（如资助关系、股权、咨询安排）、个人性的（如家庭或密切私人关系），也可能是专业性的（如竞争关系、既有承诺）。',
    'All researchers affiliated with the Institute must disclose any actual or potential conflicts of interest to the Institute\'s leadership before commencing research, submitting publications, or participating in governance activities. Disclosures must be updated if circumstances change.': '所有与研究院建立学术关联的研究者，在开展研究、提交出版成果或参与治理活动前，均须向研究院领导层披露任何实际或潜在利益冲突。情况发生变化时须更新披露。',
    'Amendments to the Institute Charter require approval by Panorama Scholarly Group. Amendments to governance policies require approval by the Institute\'s leadership. Approval must be documented in writing.': '研究院章程修订须经全景学术集团批准。治理政策修订须经研究院领导层批准。批准过程须形成书面记录。',
    'Approved amendments are published on the Institute\'s website as soon as practicable following approval. The version history of the Charter and governance documents is maintained for transparency.': '修订获批后，应尽快在研究院网站发布。章程和治理文件的版本历史应予保存，以确保透明度。',
    'Approved amendments take effect from the date specified in the approval document. Where an effective date is not specified, the amendment takes effect 30 days after the date of approval.': '已批准修订自批准文件载明日期起生效；未载明生效日期的，自批准日期后 30 日起生效。',

    'All active and in-development research projects across Panorama Research Institute\'s four research centers.': '全景研究院四个研究中心正在开展和开发中的全部研究项目。',
    'All downloadable resources from Panorama Research Institute, including publications, forms, templates, guidelines, and institutional documents.': '全景研究院提供的全部可下载资源，包括出版成果、表格、模板、指南和机构文件。',
    'All forms are available as online web forms accessible via the links below. PDF versions are also available for download where indicated. Online form submissions are preferred.': '所有表格均提供在线填写版本，可通过下方链接访问。标明处也可下载 PDF 版本。优先建议在线提交。',
    'Application forms, submission forms, and inquiry forms for Panorama Research Institute\'s fellowship, collaboration, publication, and event programs.': '全景研究院研究员、合作、出版和活动项目使用的申请表、提交表和咨询表。',
    'All templates are provided in Microsoft Word format (.docx) for ease of editing. If you require a template in a different format (e.g., LaTeX or Google Docs), please contact the Publications Unit at': '所有模板均以 Microsoft Word（.docx）格式提供，便于编辑。如需其他格式（如 LaTeX 或 Google Docs），请联系出版部门：',
    'Need a resource not listed here?': '需要未列出的资源？',
    'Contact the Institute to request additional templates, forms, or guidance documents.': '请联系研究院索取其他模板、表格或指南文件。',
    'Detailed guidelines for preparing full-length research report submissions, including structure, formatting, data presentation, and ethical disclosure requirements.': '关于完整研究报告提交准备的详细指南，包括结构、格式、数据呈现和伦理披露要求。',
