    'Begin planning for the Center for Arts, Culture and Embodiment': '开始规划艺术、文化与具身研究中心',
    'Expand the POSI database to become a recognized global resource': '将 POSI 数据库拓展为获得认可的全球性资源',
    'Expand the POSI database to a broader range of scholarly journals': '将 POSI 数据库扩展至更广泛的学术期刊',
    'Introduce training programs for journal editors and research teams': '推出面向期刊编辑和研究团队的培训项目',
    'Build a community of practice around the Institute\'s research themes': '围绕研究院研究主题建设实践共同体',
    'Officially launch the POSI database and begin public access operations': '正式上线 POSI 数据库并启动公众访问运营',
    'Establish the Center for Education and Learning Research (fifth center)': '设立教育与学习研究中心（第五个中心）',
    'Launch the Institute\'s collaboration and fellowship application processes': '启动研究院合作与研究员申请流程',
    'Establish the Institute\'s governance framework, charter, and core policies': '建立研究院治理框架、章程和核心政策',
    'Achieve a sustained annual publication output across all publication types': '在所有出版类型中实现持续年度成果产出',
    'Establish the Center for AI and Future Society as the fourth research center': '设立人工智能与未来社会研究中心作为第四个研究中心',
    'Begin formal institutional cooperation discussions with partner institutions': '开始与伙伴机构进行正式机构合作讨论',
    'Establish all six research centers and bring each to full operational capacity': '设立全部六个研究中心，并使各中心达到完整运营能力',
    'Produce and publish the first full-length research reports from active projects': '产出并发布进行中项目的首批完整研究报告',
    'Develop a recognized and regularly cited journal and policy evaluation framework': '开发获得认可并被持续引用的期刊与政策评价框架',
    'Launch the first Institute-edited volume in partnership with an academic publisher': '与学术出版社合作推出首部研究院主编文集',
    'Expand the research fellow network to include scholars from at least five countries': '将研究员网络扩展至至少五个国家的学者',
    'Develop a major conference series on scholarly communication and academic publishing': '发展关于学术传播和学术出版的重要会议系列',
    'Establish a multi-year research grant program in collaboration with partner institutions': '与伙伴机构合作建立多年期研究资助项目',
    'Establish formal institutional cooperation agreements with at least three partner institutions': '与至少三个伙伴机构建立正式机构合作协议',
    'Establish three initial research centers: Scholarly Publishing Studies, Scholarly Indexing and Evaluation, and Policy and Social Research': '设立三个初始研究中心：学术出版研究、学术索引与评价、政策与社会研究',
    'The phased development plan of Panorama Research Institute, outlining priorities, milestones, and targets across a multi-year horizon.': '全景研究院的阶段性发展计划，概述多年周期内的优先事项、里程碑和目标。',
    'Panorama Research Institute follows a phased development approach, building institutional capacity progressively while maintaining high standards of academic quality and governance. The roadmap below outlines the key milestones, priorities, and expected outputs for each phase.': '全景研究院采取阶段性发展方式，在保持高标准学术质量和治理要求的同时逐步建设机构能力。下方路线图概述各阶段的关键里程碑、优先事项和预期成果。',

    'Begin annual reports': '启动年度报告',
    'Expand to six research centers': '拓展至六个研究中心',
    'Initiate first research projects': '启动首批研究项目',
    'Publish inaugural working papers': '发布创始工作论文',
    'Launch three core research centers': '启动三个核心研究中心',
    'Broader policy advisory activities': '更广泛的政策咨询活动',
    'Establish scholar and fellowship programs': '建立学者与研究员项目',
    'Establish Institute governance and charter': '建立研究院治理体系和章程',
    'Operate and expand the POSI scholarly indexing platform after launch': 'POSI 学术索引平台上线后持续运营并拓展',
    'The Institute\'s research activities are organized across six primary research areas.': '研究院的研究活动围绕六个主要研究领域组织。',
    'Panorama Research Institute is the internal research and academic development division of Panorama Scholarly Group. It operates as an independent academic platform, providing research support, publication services, and scholarly infrastructure to the broader PSG ecosystem.': '全景研究院是全景学术集团内部研究与学术发展部门。研究院作为独立学术平台运行，为更广泛的 PSG 生态系统提供研究支持、出版服务和学术基础设施。',
    'The internal organizational structure of Panorama Research Institute, including its administrative units, research centers, and academic programs.': '全景研究院的内部组织架构，包括行政单元、研究中心和学术项目。',
    'The Publications Unit manages the editorial, production, and dissemination processes for all Institute publications, including research reports, working papers, policy briefs, edited volumes, and the annual report.': '出版单元负责管理研究院所有出版成果的编辑、制作和传播流程，包括研究报告、工作论文、政策简报、主编文集和年度报告。',
    'The Academic Events Unit plans and manages the Institute\'s program of conferences, seminars, workshops, and training programs. It coordinates calls for papers and chapters, manages registration and logistics, and produces event proceedings where applicable.': '学术活动单元负责规划和管理研究院的会议、研讨会、工作坊和培训项目，协调论文和章节征集，管理注册与会务，并在适用情况下制作活动论文集。',
    'The Collaboration Office manages the Institute\'s external partnership activities, including institutional cooperation agreements, research project proposals from external parties, edited volume and special issue proposals, and event co-organization requests.': '合作办公室负责管理研究院对外伙伴关系活动，包括机构合作协议、外部研究项目提案、主编文集和特刊提案，以及活动联合组织申请。',
    'The Scholar and Fellowship Program manages the recruitment, onboarding, and support of research fellows, associate research fellows, visiting scholars, and research assistants. It maintains scholar profiles and coordinates with research centers on scholar assignments.': '学者与研究员项目负责研究员、副研究员、访问学者和研究助理的招募、入职和支持，维护学者档案，并与研究中心协调学者分配。',
    'The Institute Office is responsible for overall administration, governance compliance, communications, human resources, and coordination between units. It maintains the Institute\'s official records, manages institutional correspondence, and serves as the primary point of contact for external inquiries.': '研究院办公室负责整体行政、治理合规、传播、人力资源以及各单元之间的协调，维护研究院正式记录，管理机构往来，并作为外部咨询的主要联系点。',
    'The Research Centers are the primary academic units of the Institute. Each center has a defined thematic mandate, a dedicated director, and a team of affiliated researchers. Centers develop and manage research projects, produce publications, organize events, and build partnerships relevant to their domain.': '研究中心是研究院的主要学术单元。每个中心都有明确的主题任务、专门主任和关联研究团队。各中心开发和管理研究项目、产出出版成果、组织活动，并建设与其领域相关的伙伴关系。',

