    'Establish all six research centers and bring each to full operational capacity': '設立全部六個研究中心，並使各中心達到完整營運能力',
    'Produce and publish the first full-length research reports from active projects': '產出並發布進行中項目的首批完整研究報告',
    'Develop a recognized and regularly cited journal and policy evaluation framework': '開發獲得認可並被持續引用的期刊與政策評價框架',
    'Launch the first Institute-edited volume in partnership with an academic publisher': '與學術出版社合作推出首部研究院主編文集',
    'Expand the research fellow network to include scholars from at least five countries': '將研究員網路擴展至至少五個國家的學者',
    'Develop a major conference series on scholarly communication and academic publishing': '發展關於學術傳播和學術出版的重要會議系列',
    'Establish a multi-year research grant program in collaboration with partner institutions': '與夥伴機構合作建立多年期研究資助項目',
    'Establish formal institutional cooperation agreements with at least three partner institutions': '與至少三個夥伴機構建立正式機構合作協議',
    'Establish three initial research centers: Scholarly Publishing Studies, Scholarly Indexing and Evaluation, and Policy and Social Research': '設立三個初始研究中心：學術出版研究、學術索引與評價、政策與社會研究',
    'The phased development plan of Panorama Research Institute, outlining priorities, milestones, and targets across a multi-year horizon.': '全景研究院的階段性發展計畫，概述多年週期內的優先事項、里程碑和目標。',
    'Panorama Research Institute follows a phased development approach, building institutional capacity progressively while maintaining high standards of academic quality and governance. The roadmap below outlines the key milestones, priorities, and expected outputs for each phase.': '全景研究院採取階段性發展方式，在保持高標準學術品質和治理要求的同時逐步建設機構能力。下方路線圖概述各階段的關鍵里程碑、優先事項和預期成果。',
    'Begin annual reports': '啟動年度報告',
    'Expand to six research centers': '拓展至六個研究中心',
    'Initiate first research projects': '啟動首批研究項目',
    'Publish inaugural working papers': '發布創始工作論文',
    'Launch three core research centers': '啟動三個核心研究中心',
    'Broader policy advisory activities': '更廣泛的政策諮詢活動',
    'Establish scholar and fellowship programs': '建立學者與研究員項目',
    'Establish Institute governance and charter': '建立研究院治理體系和章程',
    'Operate and expand the POSI scholarly indexing platform after launch': 'POSI 學術索引平台上線後持續營運並拓展',
    'The Institute\'s research activities are organized across six primary research areas.': '研究院的研究活動圍繞六個主要研究領域組織。',
    'Panorama Research Institute is the internal research and academic development division of Panorama Scholarly Group. It operates as an independent academic platform, providing research support, publication services, and scholarly infrastructure to the broader PSG ecosystem.': '全景研究院是全景學術集團內部研究與學術發展部門。研究院作為獨立學術平台運行，為更廣泛的 PSG 生態系統提供研究支持、出版服務和學術基礎設施。',
    'The internal organizational structure of Panorama Research Institute, including its administrative units, research centers, and academic programs.': '全景研究院的內部組織架構，包括行政單元、研究中心和學術項目。',
    'The Publications Unit manages the editorial, production, and dissemination processes for all Institute publications, including research reports, working papers, policy briefs, edited volumes, and the annual report.': '出版單元負責管理研究院所有出版成果的編輯、製作和傳播流程，包括研究報告、工作論文、政策簡報、主編文集和年度報告。',
    'The Academic Events Unit plans and manages the Institute\'s program of conferences, seminars, workshops, and training programs. It coordinates calls for papers and chapters, manages registration and logistics, and produces event proceedings where applicable.': '學術活動單元負責規劃和管理研究院的會議、研討會、工作坊和培訓項目，協調論文和章節徵集，管理註冊與會務，並在適用情況下製作活動論文集。',
    'The Collaboration Office manages the Institute\'s external partnership activities, including institutional cooperation agreements, research project proposals from external parties, edited volume and special issue proposals, and event co-organization requests.': '合作辦公室負責管理研究院對外夥伴關係活動，包括機構合作協議、外部研究項目提案、主編文集和特刊提案，以及活動聯合組織申請。',
    'The Scholar and Fellowship Program manages the recruitment, onboarding, and support of research fellows, associate research fellows, visiting scholars, and research assistants. It maintains scholar profiles and coordinates with research centers on scholar assignments.': '學者與研究員項目負責研究員、副研究員、訪問學者和研究助理的招募、入職和支持，維護學者檔案，並與研究中心協調學者分配。',
    'The Institute Office is responsible for overall administration, governance compliance, communications, human resources, and coordination between units. It maintains the Institute\'s official records, manages institutional correspondence, and serves as the primary point of contact for external inquiries.': '研究院辦公室負責整體行政、治理合規、傳播、人力資源以及各單元之間的協調，維護研究院正式記錄，管理機構往來，並作為外部諮詢的主要聯絡點。',
    'The Research Centers are the primary academic units of the Institute. Each center has a defined thematic mandate, a dedicated director, and a team of affiliated researchers. Centers develop and manage research projects, produce publications, organize events, and build partnerships relevant to their domain.': '研究中心是研究院的主要學術單元。每個中心都有明確的主題任務、專門主任和關聯研究團隊。各中心開發和管理研究項目、產出出版成果、組織活動，並建設與其領域相關的夥伴關係。',

